# 🔄 PART 4: UPDATED KEY SEQUENCE DIAGRAM (Submit Report with Deadline Logic)

```plantuml
@startuml Submit_Report_With_Deadline_Sequence
!theme plain
autonumber

actor "Cell Leader" as CL
participant "Flutter App" as App
participant "Hive (Local DB)" as Hive
participant "FastAPI Backend" as API
participant "PostgreSQL" as DB
participant "Appwrite Storage" as Storage
participant "FCM Service" as FCM

CL -> App: Fill report form\n(Meeting on Wednesday Mar 12)
activate App

CL -> App: Select 1-2 photos
App -> App: Compress photos

CL -> App: Tap "Submit"\n(Thursday Mar 13, 3pm)
App -> App: Validate form data

App -> App: Calculate submission deadline:\nSunday Mar 16, 9am

App -> App: Calculate week boundaries:\nweek_start = Mon Mar 10\nweek_end = Sun Mar 16

App -> Hive: Save draft\n(in case of failure)
activate Hive
Hive --> App: Draft saved
deactivate Hive

App -> Storage: Upload photos
activate Storage
Storage --> App: Photo URLs
deactivate Storage

App -> API: POST /api/reports\n{\n  meetingDate: "2026-03-12",\n  weekStartDate: "2026-03-10",\n  weekEndDate: "2026-03-16",\n  actualMeetingDay: "WEDNESDAY",\n  submissionDeadline: "2026-03-16T09:00:00Z",\n  photoUrls: ["url1", "url2"],\n  ...\n}
activate API

API -> API: Validate report data
API -> API: Check duplicate:\nWHERE cell_id = ? AND week_start_date = ?

alt No duplicate
  API -> API: Determine status:\nIF NOW() <= submission_deadline\n  THEN "SUBMITTED"\nELSE "LATE"
  
  note right
    Submitted at: Mar 13, 3pm
    Deadline: Mar 16, 9am
    Status: SUBMITTED (on time)
  end note
  
  API -> DB: INSERT INTO cell_reports\n(..., status = 'SUBMITTED')
  activate DB
  DB --> API: Report created (UUID)
  deactivate DB
  
  API -> DB: DELETE FROM sync_queue\nWHERE user_id = ?
  
  API -> API: Check if Senior Cell Leader\nneeds notification
  
  API -> FCM: Send notification to SCL:\n"Cell 1A submitted weekly report"
  activate FCM
  FCM --> API: Notification sent
  deactivate FCM
  
  API --> App: 201 Created\n{\n  id: uuid,\n  status: "SUBMITTED",\n  submittedAt: "2026-03-13T15:00:00Z",\n  deadline: "2026-03-16T09:00:00Z"\n}
  
  App -> Hive: Delete draft
  App --> CL: Show success:\n"Report submitted on time!\nDeadline: Sunday 9am"
  
else Report for this week already exists
  API --> App: 400 Bad Request\n{error: "Report already exists for this week"}
  App --> CL: Show error
  
end

deactivate API
deactivate App

note over CL, FCM
  LATE SUBMISSION SCENARIO:
  If Cell Leader submits on Sunday Mar 16 at 10am
  (1 hour after deadline), status = "LATE"
  
  OVERDUE SCENARIO:
  If no submission by Sunday 9am, a cron job
  marks the report as "OVERDUE" and sends
  alert to Fellowship Pastor.
end note

@enduml
```

